sequenceDiagram
    participant Op as Operator
    participant CatalogAPI as Catalog API
    participant ProductDomain as Product Domain
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant Inventory as inventory BC
    participant Orders as orders BC

    Op ->> CatalogAPI: PATCH /products/{id}/activate
    CatalogAPI ->> ProductDomain: activate()
    ProductDomain ->> ProductDomain: verify CAT-RULE-002 (not DISCONTINUED)
    ProductDomain ->> ProductDomain: verify CAT-RULE-001 (category ACTIVE)
    ProductDomain ->> ProductDomain: transition status -> ACTIVE
    ProductDomain -->> CatalogAPI: OK
    CatalogAPI ->> MQ: publish ProductActivated (catalog.product.activated)
    MQ ->> Inventory: ProductActivated consumed
    MQ ->> Orders: ProductActivated consumed
    CatalogAPI -->> Op: 204 No Content
